1.Make the "assignment2" folder as the present working directory in the terminal.
2.Run "make all" command.
3.Run the executable "./test.out".

Instructions to use:
i) Use "LEFT ARROW","RIGHT ARROW","UP ARROW" and "DOWN ARROW" keys to TRANSLATE the model left,right,up and down respectively.	

ii) Use "+/-" keys to SCALE the model (default scaling: 1.1 and 0.9).

iii) While viewing the model, use the "LEFT MOUSE BUTTON" to rotate.
   The model will be rotated about the centroid and by an amount defined by the arc between the two clicked points.  
iv) Default window size is 1000 x 650. Resize to fullscreen for convenience.	
  
 
